Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.74,0:00:04.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,☆Dragon Ball Super☆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.61,0:00:14.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,曾经淡忘的梦想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:14.84,0:00:19.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,如今再续前缘　又开始燃亮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:20.52,0:00:24.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,给星星都连上线
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:24.85,0:00:28.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就这样给宇宙画出了门框
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:30.44,0:00:34.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,跻身于全新的舞台上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:35.45,0:00:40.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,向诸神发出挑战
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:40.62,0:00:42.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强烈☆猛烈☆活力满泻！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:42.66,0:00:45.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Let's Go！Go！恐慌奔走！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:45.17,0:00:49.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你输了就能变更强
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:49.88,0:00:55.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不知天高地厚又何妨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:55.55,0:01:00.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,生无可悔　身无界限　一往无前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:00.51,0:01:02.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,壮烈☆激烈☆活力爆裂！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:02.64,0:01:05.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Let's Go！Yes！拳脚不绝！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:05.14,0:01:09.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,去沐浴颤抖的感觉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:09.90,0:01:13.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一个壮大传说　正在等着你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:29.05,0:01:32.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,格斗比赛终于拉开帷幕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:33.39,0:01:36.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,悟空等人奔赴无名星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:36.52,0:01:41.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,亲眼目睹排列在宇宙空间中的巨大龙珠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:41.32,0:01:43.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不…不敢相信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.40,0:01:47.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那就是超级龙珠吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.96,0:02:04.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,第6宇宙的选手已经抵达会场
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.05,0:02:08.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,等待悟空等人的到来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.76,0:02:13.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,居然还有这样的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.06,0:02:16.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,看起来像机器人其实是人类吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.10,0:02:17.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.60,0:02:20.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是弗利萨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.65,0:02:22.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在他们的宇宙里也有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.15,0:02:25.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,还有个像熊一样的家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.78,0:02:30.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,以地球的命运作为赌注的战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.57,0:02:33.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,即将拉开帷幕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.73,0:02:55.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,「震惊吧第6宇宙！这就是超级赛亚人孙悟空！」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.99,0:03:11.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你这家伙身体庞大，脚步倒是很灵活啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.86,0:03:15.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,破坏神选拔格斗比赛终于开始了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.66,0:03:19.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,两位选手像是在试探对手一样，旨在稳中求胜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.19,0:03:51.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,小心追击，悟空！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.99,0:04:01.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,刚才是个好机会啊，怎么不攻过来？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.38,0:04:06.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,伯达摩选手，从容不迫！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.63,0:04:08.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,实力惊人，第6宇宙！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.84,0:04:10.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,相比之下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.03,0:04:12.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,孙悟空选手表现得差强人意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.80,0:04:15.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎么办？第7宇宙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.39,0:04:20.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哎呀哎呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.77,0:04:24.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他这点水平早就在比鲁斯城见识过了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.19,0:04:27.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,同是赛亚人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.19,0:04:31.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,第6宇宙和第7宇宙的差别居然这么大啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.69,0:04:33.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,象帕大人告诉过我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.53,0:04:35.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,说你没什么了不起的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.28,0:04:39.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,结果比我想象得还要差
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.41,0:04:41.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,第7宇宙的小哥啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.33,0:04:43.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你怎么了？悟空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.96,0:04:48.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,烤肉吃多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.38,0:04:56.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一二三四
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.34,0:04:57.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不妙啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.59,0:05:01.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,得快点把肚子里的食物消化掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.14,0:05:06.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,孙悟空选手竟然说他吃多了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.69,0:05:09.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他到底吃了多少烤肉？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.78,0:05:13.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,算了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.57,0:05:16.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我就帮你消化一下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.49,0:05:20.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,正好有助消化
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.12,0:05:23.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要的就是这个感觉，继续来啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.34,0:05:38.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.89,0:05:41.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这小子真让人为他捏一把汗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.81,0:05:45.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这是怎么搞的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.02,0:05:49.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,接下来才是伯达摩的拿手好戏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.61,0:05:54.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.16,0:06:05.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,成功了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.65,0:06:42.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,悟…悟空的攻击，完全没奏效
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.32,0:06:44.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那只熊的身体到底是什么做的啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.99,0:06:46.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不仅如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.38,0:06:48.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那家伙的脚连动都没动一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.13,0:06:54.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,受到的伤害全都传送到异次元空间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.63,0:06:56.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,让攻击彻底失效
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.38,0:06:57.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.34,0:06:59.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯，大概是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.76,0:07:02.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大概啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.02,0:07:13.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,老孙现在反而处于下风
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.86,0:07:17.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这招如何！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.03,0:07:25.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哎呀，看来形势不太妙啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.20,0:07:28.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,继续进攻，别停手！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.25,0:07:29.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.79,0:07:34.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,连击也不起作用啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.09,0:07:37.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这可怎么办才好？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.80,0:07:42.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,卡卡罗特，你白长脑袋了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.14,0:07:45.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我懂了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.64,0:07:50.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,说你白长脑袋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.10,0:07:52.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可不是让你这么用吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.19,0:07:54.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,诶？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.02,0:07:58.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,看我…撂倒你！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.45,0:08:04.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,果然轻松地就撂倒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.70,0:08:08.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你太依仗让攻击失效，没有努力修炼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.33,0:08:10.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,放…放开我！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.50,0:08:11.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,还不放开！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.57,0:08:46.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,比赛结束！出界！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.91,0:08:50.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,第7宇宙的孙悟空选手获胜！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.83,0:08:54.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.58,0:08:56.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不愧是悟空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.96,0:08:58.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,原来如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.13,0:09:00.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,格斗比赛是有规则的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.63,0:09:03.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,让对手出界一样是赢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.05,0:09:05.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好样的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.05,0:09:10.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,如果不是在比赛里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.39,0:09:12.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可能输的人就是我了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.52,0:09:14.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,卑鄙小人！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.69,0:09:17.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你故意装出一幅很弱的样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.65,0:09:19.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好让我放松警惕！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.82,0:09:21.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我才没有呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.11,0:09:23.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,因为上次见到你的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.49,0:09:27.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,维斯先生做给我穿的练功服很重而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.20,0:09:29.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,还有那个像大激光一样的光线道具
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.12,0:09:32.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,又如何解释！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.91,0:09:35.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那不是武器，而是从身体里发出来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.91,0:09:37.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所以并没有犯规
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.92,0:09:39.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,而且伯达摩选手也用了那招
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.96,0:09:41.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,反正不能算数！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.17,0:09:44.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,刚才的比赛得重比一次！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.97,0:09:46.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,太不像样了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.51,0:09:47.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就是，就是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.09,0:09:50.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,根本没有犯规！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.18,0:09:53.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你怎么像个任性的小孩似的没完没了啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.68,0:09:56.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你还算是个神吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.14,0:09:57.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,请少说两句吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.36,0:10:10.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可恶，可恶…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.95,0:10:14.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,象帕大人，我们没有必要一场不输
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.70,0:10:17.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我们还有四位选手呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.12,0:10:20.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,而且，下一位选手是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.63,0:10:32.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,初战告捷的孙选手下一个对手是弗罗斯特选手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.10,0:10:38.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,终于到你了，第6宇宙的弗利萨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.05,0:11:09.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我有一种不祥的预感
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.34,0:11:11.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这张脸真让人不爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.68,0:11:12.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.55,0:11:15.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,连声音都一样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.23,0:11:19.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,打得好精彩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.81,0:11:23.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,能和你这样厉害的战士比赛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.90,0:11:25.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我感到十分荣幸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.98,0:11:27.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,还请你多多指教
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.70,0:11:30.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,请多指教
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.41,0:11:37.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,第7宇宙的各位绅士、淑女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.16,0:11:41.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,十分遗憾，我们不得不分成敌我双方对战
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.00,0:11:44.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是，这毕竟只是格斗比赛而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.00,0:11:48.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我相信，比赛结束后，我们会手握着手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.51,0:11:51.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,彼此珍视此次的邂逅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.01,0:11:55.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,敬请各位欣赏我们的比赛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.93,0:11:58.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,谢谢大家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.44,0:12:04.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这边的这位弗利萨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.23,0:12:06.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真是大不相同啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.07,0:12:11.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我从来都没想象过变成好人的弗利萨是什么样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.53,0:12:13.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这可如何是好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.28,0:12:18.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,比赛开始！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.54,0:12:21.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,来啊，让我见识一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.51,0:12:41.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这是什么招数啊，吓我一跳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.52,0:12:43.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真是抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.02,0:12:46.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,本来我是想从正面出击的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.31,0:12:47.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可是考虑到体型的差距
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.98,0:12:51.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,轻量级也有轻量级的套路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.11,0:12:55.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎么了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.16,0:12:59.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你好像是在试探我的实力啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.62,0:13:02.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,快变身吧，变成最终形态
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.25,0:13:03.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.04,0:13:05.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,宇宙虽然不同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.54,0:13:07.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,毕竟是这个宇宙的弗利萨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.71,0:13:10.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你是打算试探对手的实力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.80,0:13:12.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,再逐步变身吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.67,0:13:14.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你怎么知道？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.97,0:13:17.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在我的宇宙里有个人和你很像
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.64,0:13:19.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我和他交过手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.47,0:13:20.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,原来如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.60,0:13:22.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是这么回事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.43,0:13:23.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你不拿出全力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.73,0:13:26.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,稍不留心可能就会被干掉喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.90,0:13:28.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,多谢你的忠告
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.69,0:13:29.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.82,0:13:32.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我就变身成最终形态吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.79,0:13:50.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这就是我的最终形态
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.34,0:13:57.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那家伙居然会变身啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.80,0:14:00.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那个混账，这根本不是最终形态
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.14,0:14:02.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,装傻充愣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.89,0:14:04.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这样就行了吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.68,0:14:06.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,也罢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.39,0:14:08.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,和我认识的家伙不太一样就是了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.69,0:14:13.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,顺便问一句，在你的宇宙里，我打赢你了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.15,0:14:16.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我看你还是不问为好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.61,0:14:17.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.15,0:14:20.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,希望我不会重蹈覆辙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.78,0:14:22.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我也希望如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.04,0:14:24.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,接招！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.45,0:15:02.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,太…太厉害了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.83,0:15:06.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,根据刚刚得到的消息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.20,0:15:09.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,弗罗斯特选手刚才展示的变身
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.08,0:15:11.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,被称为突击形态
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.79,0:15:16.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,为了彻底平息第6宇宙的战乱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.76,0:15:19.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,弗罗斯特选手率领和平维持军
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.63,0:15:22.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,攻入纷争地带时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.89,0:15:26.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,正是变身为这个突击形态
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.72,0:15:29.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,弗罗斯特选手在战争结束后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.35,0:15:32.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,也不遗余力地帮助当地重建，支援受难儿童
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.23,0:15:35.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,并三次获得宇宙和平奖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.07,0:15:38.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是个大好人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.57,0:15:40.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,象帕大人招揽他的时候说过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.70,0:15:43.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,如果他赢了比赛就会支援他的活动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.99,0:15:45.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,输了的话就不支援了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.33,0:15:47.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,当然了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.79,0:15:49.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那太可怜了吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.66,0:15:51.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,身为破坏神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.16,0:15:53.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是不能说这种话的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.63,0:15:56.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,同一张脸，不同宇宙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.75,0:15:59.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,差别竟然会这么大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.13,0:16:01.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这下好了，我都不知道该为谁加油了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.97,0:16:04.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这还用说吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.09,0:16:06.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,悟空，别输啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.05,0:16:08.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,爸爸，加油啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.06,0:16:17.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哎呀哎呀，看来是我们宇宙的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.94,0:16:21.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,弗罗斯特占了上风啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.78,0:16:25.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那可不好说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.34,0:16:39.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,糟糕，做得有点过火了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.34,0:16:45.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,多亏了你，我终于进入状态了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.05,0:16:48.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我一向慢热的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.18,0:16:49.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,多谢啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.31,0:16:51.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你竟然还没使出全力？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.48,0:16:54.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这可真是吓了我一跳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.15,0:16:59.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你这家伙真可恶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.77,0:17:01.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可恶？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.40,0:17:04.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你还藏着一个阶段的变身吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.24,0:17:08.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是为了后面的比赛故意保存实力的吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.95,0:17:10.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你有什么根据？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.24,0:17:13.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,因为我就是这样的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.63,0:17:23.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什么？喂，告诉我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.72,0:17:25.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,赛亚人能变身的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.01,0:17:26.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.05,0:17:30.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,从来没听说过，更没见过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.14,0:17:35.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,第6宇宙看好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.81,0:17:38.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这就是超级赛亚人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.52,0:17:40.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我不会再手下留情了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.23,0:17:44.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我们都使出全力，拼个痛快吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.44,0:17:47.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你也快变成最终形态吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.03,0:17:52.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我之所以不变成真正的最终形态
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.49,0:17:55.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不是因为像你说的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.29,0:17:57.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,为了保存实力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.55,0:18:07.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎么了，怎么了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.06,0:18:15.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,最终形态的力量很难控制
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.10,0:18:21.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,为此，我曾经误杀了一个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.40,0:18:23.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没有必要杀掉的坏人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.36,0:18:28.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,从那以后，我就封印了最终形态
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.82,0:18:30.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,悟空先生，如果是你的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.99,0:18:34.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,应该能承受得住我的最终形态
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.79,0:18:37.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没错，快放马过来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.66,0:18:40.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,能和你交手真是太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.13,0:18:41.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,接招！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.88,0:18:49.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这就是我的全部力量！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.62,0:19:22.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哎呀哎呀，形势一下子就逆转了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.75,0:19:26.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,想不到你这么厉害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.35,0:19:42.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这就是你的全部力量吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.11,0:19:46.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你看起来像是个好人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.44,0:19:48.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所以我不想让你受重伤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.78,0:19:50.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我劝你还是趁早投降为好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.86,0:19:53.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,多谢你的忠告
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.91,0:19:56.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不过，这是不可能的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.66,0:20:02.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,为了世界的和平，我必须赢得比赛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.87,0:20:06.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,让象帕大人助我一臂之力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.23,0:20:23.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我看不下去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.06,0:20:26.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,弗罗斯特也不要输啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.36,0:20:27.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,布玛小姐？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.77,0:20:28.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没办法啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.07,0:20:35.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,永远不要放弃，要振作起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.74,0:20:39.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这是我鼓励孩子们时说过的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.16,0:20:42.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我要对说过的话负责任
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.31,0:21:09.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,有破绽！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:17.12,0:21:18.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.74,0:21:19.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:45.58,0:21:48.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,永别了亲爱的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:48.38,0:21:56.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,淡红的天空下的我和你　我站在你右边　而你待在我的左边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.47,0:22:00.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,「我很喜欢你　这一生都不会忘记你」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:00.97,0:22:06.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,想说出口　又咽了回去　不如还是　把话埋在心底
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:06.35,0:22:11.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,突然两人被困在　一场滂沱落花雨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:11.57,0:22:16.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,簌簌的　谱成一首动人旋律
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:16.65,0:22:21.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,至少把你的身影　从我的眼前隐去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:22.04,0:22:26.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,渐染一片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:23.66,0:22:26.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,淡红色
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:24.87,0:22:26.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,的情绪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:27.29,0:22:33.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,渐染一片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:29.08,0:22:33.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,永别时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:30.17,0:22:33.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,的回忆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:37.74,0:22:39.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗨！我是悟空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:39.66,0:22:40.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什么，什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:41.07,0:22:42.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他用了什么招数？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:42.70,0:22:44.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我完全没搞明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:44.95,0:22:48.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,比鲁斯大人在笑，表情却很可怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:48.92,0:22:52.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,脱掉披风后的比克感觉就是不一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:52.84,0:22:54.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哦！是那招！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:54.96,0:22:56.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,下集『龙珠超』
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:56.96,0:23:01.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,「比克VS弗罗斯特 孤注一掷的魔贯光杀炮！」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:01.34,0:23:02.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一定要看啊

